title: Gelish Soak Off 0.5 oz Ooca Coocha Bing Bang Bam Gel Nail Color Harmony Polish
description: These gels come in an array of fun colors. It applies like polish, with twist cap and applicator, but are cured in a LED lamp in 30 seconds or in 2 minutes in traditional UV lamps. Gelish stays on nails for three weeks with no chipping or peeling, and soak completely off in only 15 minutes.
